1
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:15,000
[ MAN ]
ETERNAL LIFE YOU SAY?

2
00:00:15,033 --> 00:00:17,333
[ MEPHISTO ]
CORRECT. YOU'LL BE ABLE
TO EXPERIENCE...

3
00:00:17,366 --> 00:00:20,800
ALL THE PLEASURES AND SORROWS
THIS WORLD HAS TO OFFER...

4
00:00:20,833 --> 00:00:23,500
THROUGHOUT ETERNITY EVER AFTER.

5
00:00:23,533 --> 00:00:28,033
BUT IF YOU GROW TIRED
OF YOUR IMMORTALITY
AND WISH FOR IT TO END,

6
00:00:28,066 --> 00:00:31,700
THEN I BECOME THE NEW OWNER
OF YOUR POOR SOUL.

7
00:00:31,733 --> 00:00:34,000
ARE THOSE TERMS ACCEPTABLE?

8
00:00:34,033 --> 00:00:36,900
INTERESTING.

9
00:00:36,933 --> 00:00:39,666
VERY WELL.
I ACCEPT YOUR WAGER.

10
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:42,400
[ BELL TOLLING ]

11
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:48,100
THE CONTRACT IS SEALED.

12
00:00:48,133 --> 00:00:50,533
NOW THEN,
I BID YOU ADIEU.

13
00:00:50,566 --> 00:00:54,166
EINS, ZWEI, DREI.

14
00:01:12,933 --> 00:01:15,166
♪ [ MEN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

15
00:02:32,899 --> 00:02:34,499
[ ROARING ]

16
00:02:39,532 --> 00:02:41,899
- [ GRUNTS ]
- RIN!

17
00:02:41,932 --> 00:02:43,399
I'M GOOD.

18
00:02:43,432 --> 00:02:45,532
JUST A LITTLE SCRATCH,
IS ALL.

19
00:02:49,132 --> 00:02:50,799
[ GRUNTING ]

20
00:02:52,532 --> 00:02:54,199
WHAT'S THAT?

21
00:02:54,232 --> 00:02:55,865
IT'S A DIMENSIONAL TEAR.

22
00:02:55,899 --> 00:03:00,965
MY GUESS IS HE'S EXPANDING
THE GATE TILL IT'S BIG ENOUGH
TO SWALLOW ASSIAH.

23
00:03:00,999 --> 00:03:04,932
I'VE BEEN DREAMING
OF THIS MOMENT
FOR THE LAST 15 YEARS.

24
00:03:04,965 --> 00:03:10,232
THE DAY I FINALLY GET TO BRING
THE WORLDS OF ASSIAH AND GEHENNA
TOGETHER AND CREATE A NEW EARTH.

25
00:03:10,265 --> 00:03:14,199
[ THINKING ]
WE CAN'T LET THAT HAPPEN.
WE HAVE TO STOP HIM.

26
00:03:14,232 --> 00:03:16,132
- [ GROWLING ]
- [ GRUNTING ]

27
00:03:20,399 --> 00:03:22,932
[ GASPS ]
RIN! YUKI!

28
00:03:22,965 --> 00:03:25,365
[ ROARING ]

29
00:03:25,399 --> 00:03:27,499
- WATCH OUT!
- SHIEMI!

30
00:03:31,565 --> 00:03:33,132
WHAT THE--

31
00:03:33,165 --> 00:03:36,765
TO YOU, VILLAINS
WHO WOULD CRUSH
INNOCENT FLOWERS SUCH AS THESE,

32
00:03:36,799 --> 00:03:40,665
I, ARTHUR AUGUSTE ANGEL,
SHALL DELIVER JUSTICE.

33
00:03:40,699 --> 00:03:42,565
IT TOOK YA LONG ENOUGH,
BALDY!

34
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:44,599
I CAN HANDLE THIS ONE.

35
00:03:44,632 --> 00:03:47,332
JUST SIT BACK
AND WATCH THE FIREWORKS.

36
00:03:47,365 --> 00:03:48,965
HEY, DON'T TELL ME
WHAT TO DO!

37
00:03:48,999 --> 00:03:51,065
ZODIAC SLASH!

38
00:03:55,899 --> 00:03:57,132
[ GRUNTS ]

39
00:03:57,165 --> 00:03:59,032
[ GASPS ]

40
00:03:59,065 --> 00:04:00,632
[ SHOUTING ]

41
00:04:07,232 --> 00:04:08,765
[ BOTH GRUNT ]

42
00:04:08,799 --> 00:04:11,199
DAMN IT.
SEPARATE HITS WON'T WORK.

43
00:04:11,232 --> 00:04:13,399
WE HAVE TO TIME OUR ATTACKS.

44
00:04:13,432 --> 00:04:16,265
YUKIO'S RIGHT
ABOUT THAT.

45
00:04:16,299 --> 00:04:20,332
WE GOTTA WORK AS A TEAM
OR WE'LL NEVER BREAK THROUGH
THAT PROTECTIVE WALL OF STEEL.

46
00:04:20,365 --> 00:04:22,099
SURE YOU'RE UP FOR IT?

47
00:04:22,132 --> 00:04:25,965
WORRY ABOUT YOURSELF, KID.
I'M NOT AS THRASHED
AS YOU THINK I AM.

48
00:04:25,999 --> 00:04:30,565
I NEVER THOUGHT I'D JOIN
FORCES WITH THE SONS OF SATAN.
HOW REVOLTING.

49
00:04:33,332 --> 00:04:36,132
KIRIGAKURE SWORD TECHNIQUE,

50
00:04:36,165 --> 00:04:37,332
SNAKE BELLY!

51
00:04:37,365 --> 00:04:39,565
- [ SNARLING ]
- SNAKE FANG!

52
00:04:41,032 --> 00:04:42,832
ZODIAC SLASH!

53
00:04:49,499 --> 00:04:51,232
WHAT THE--

54
00:04:55,365 --> 00:04:57,599
[ SHOUTING ]

55
00:05:00,999 --> 00:05:02,699
WE DID IT!

56
00:05:05,865 --> 00:05:07,265
[ GASPS ]

57
00:05:07,299 --> 00:05:09,032
[ CRACKING ]

58
00:05:09,765 --> 00:05:11,565
THE HELL?
IMPOSSIBLE.

59
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:17,232
[ CRASH ]
[ GASPS ]

60
00:05:18,765 --> 00:05:19,932
RIN!

61
00:05:25,532 --> 00:05:26,932
[ GASPS ]

62
00:05:28,365 --> 00:05:31,565
[ EXPLOSIONS ]
<i>[ GASPS ]</i>

63
00:05:32,999 --> 00:05:34,699
RIN!

64
00:05:35,999 --> 00:05:37,165
RIN!

65
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:39,599
[ FOOTSTEPS RUNNING ]

66
00:05:39,632 --> 00:05:41,565
DID YOU FIND MORIYAMA?

67
00:05:41,599 --> 00:05:43,999
NOT YET.
THERE'S TOO MANY PEOPLE.

68
00:05:44,032 --> 00:05:46,299
DO YOU THINK SHE COULD BE
OUTSIDE WITH OKUMURA?

69
00:05:46,332 --> 00:05:48,165
HUH?
[ POUNDING ]

70
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:50,999
WHAT'S THAT?

71
00:05:51,032 --> 00:05:53,232
[ WHIMPERING ]
THE BARRIER'S
BEEN COMPROMISED.

72
00:05:53,265 --> 00:05:56,432
WHOEVER'S AN EXORCIST,
START KILLING THOSE DEMONS.

73
00:05:56,465 --> 00:05:59,132
THE REST OF YOU,
GET AS FAR BACK AS YOU CAN.

74
00:06:01,899 --> 00:06:04,132
DAMN IT.

75
00:06:04,165 --> 00:06:07,899
THIS PLACE IS SUPPOSED
TO BE PROTECTED.
HOW THE HELL'D THEY GET IN HERE?

76
00:06:07,932 --> 00:06:10,632
I-I DON'T KNOW.
YOU THINK OKUMURA'S OKAY?

77
00:06:10,665 --> 00:06:15,899
OF COURSE HE'S OKAY.
THAT GUY, YOU COULD KILL HIM,
BUT HE JUST KEEPS COMING BACK.

78
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:36,037
[ RIN ]
YUKIO, YOU ALL RIGHT?

79
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:38,203
YEAH.

80
00:06:38,237 --> 00:06:39,603
WHAT HAPPENED TO THE GATE?

81
00:06:39,637 --> 00:06:41,203
IT'S ATTACKING THE CITY.

82
00:06:46,137 --> 00:06:48,670
I'M SORRY IT GOT TO THIS.
WHAT?

83
00:06:48,703 --> 00:06:51,970
IT'S MY FAULT. EVERYTHING.

84
00:06:52,003 --> 00:06:53,737
WHAT WAS I THINKING?

85
00:06:53,770 --> 00:06:57,937
YEAH, YOU MADE SOME MISTAKES,
AND YOU'RE SELFISH AND STUBBORN.

86
00:06:57,970 --> 00:07:00,337
HELL, YOU DON'T EVEN LOOK UP
TO YOUR BIG BROTHER.

87
00:07:00,370 --> 00:07:03,270
MAN, YOU REALLY SUCK.
[ GASPS ]

88
00:07:03,303 --> 00:07:06,570
GROWING UP, YOU NEVER SAID
A DAMN THING
ABOUT SEEING DEMONS.

89
00:07:06,603 --> 00:07:09,537
PLUS, YOU'RE THIS TEACHER,
AND A FREAKING PALADIN?

90
00:07:09,570 --> 00:07:14,437
YOU KNOW, HAVING A SUPER SMART
LITTLE BROTHER LIKE YOU
HAS BEEN A HUGE PAIN THE ASS.

91
00:07:14,470 --> 00:07:17,470
- OW!
- HAVE A LITTLE FAITH
IN ME...

92
00:07:17,503 --> 00:07:19,637
LIKE YOU DID WHEN WE WERE KIDS.

93
00:07:26,937 --> 00:07:28,403
I WILL.

94
00:07:28,437 --> 00:07:29,737
[ KURO ]
RIN!

95
00:07:29,770 --> 00:07:32,103
KURO, WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN
ALL THIS TIME?

96
00:07:32,137 --> 00:07:34,537
SORRY. I WON'T RUN AWAY AGAIN.

97
00:07:36,537 --> 00:07:41,937
AFTER ALL, I WAS THE FAMILIAR
OF SHIRO, THE MOST POWERFUL
EXORCIST EVER.

98
00:07:41,970 --> 00:07:43,903
<i>GET ON, RIN.</i>
RIGHT.

99
00:07:43,937 --> 00:07:45,137
I'LL GO TOO.
<i>HUH?</i>

100
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:46,770
NO WAY.
YOU HEARD?

101
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:50,003
MY DEMONIC POWERS
HAVE BEEN AWAKENED TOO.

102
00:07:50,037 --> 00:07:52,837
NOW I CAN HEAR KURO
LOUD AND CLEAR JUST LIKE YOU.

103
00:07:54,503 --> 00:07:56,437
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY?
MAY I?

104
00:07:57,537 --> 00:08:00,170
OKAY, LET'S ALL GO.

105
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:09,437
THE DEMON SPAWN
ARE GOING FORTH.

106
00:08:09,470 --> 00:08:12,103
[ SHURA ]
DROP THE DEMON-HUMAN STUFF.

107
00:08:12,137 --> 00:08:16,170
THOSE KIDS ARE FIGHTING HARD
BECAUSE ASSIAH'S THE PLACE
THEY CALL HOME.

108
00:08:16,203 --> 00:08:18,003
IT'S THE PLACE
WHERE SHIRO RAISED 'EM.

109
00:08:19,237 --> 00:08:22,170
[ THINKING ]
YUKI, RIN, PLEASE.

110
00:08:22,203 --> 00:08:24,670
COME BACK SAFE.

111
00:08:27,137 --> 00:08:28,903
[ BUZZING ]
[ CLAMORING ]

112
00:08:28,937 --> 00:08:30,503
THIS WAY!
HURRY!

113
00:08:33,737 --> 00:08:36,570
DAMN IT.
THESE THINGS
JUST KEEP COMING.

114
00:08:36,603 --> 00:08:38,837
I HOPE RIN
AND THE OTHERS
ARE ALL RIGHT.

115
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:41,937
LET'S SURVIVE THIS, AND WE CAN
WORRY ABOUT THE OTHERS LATER.

116
00:08:41,970 --> 00:08:43,603
LET'S GO.

117
00:08:43,637 --> 00:08:46,437
[ MAN ]
THE STRANGE BLACK MIST,
WHICH APPEARED THIS EVENING...

118
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:49,137
AROUND TRUE CROSS ACADEMY,
HAS YET TO DISPERSE.

119
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:53,470
AN EVACUATION HAS BEEN ISSUED
TO ALL RESIDENTS LIVING WITHIN
A 20-KILOMETER RADIUS--

120
00:08:53,503 --> 00:08:55,270
[ THINKING ]
EVEN IF I WENT THERE NOW,

121
00:08:55,303 --> 00:08:57,103
I WOULDN'T BE
MUCH HELP TO THEM.

122
00:08:57,137 --> 00:09:01,070
I'M BETTER OFF STAYING HERE
DOING WHAT I DO BEST.

123
00:09:01,103 --> 00:09:07,270
GOD OF THE IRONWORKS,
PLEASE WATCH OVER RYU
AND THE OTHERS FOR ME.

124
00:09:07,303 --> 00:09:09,503
[ GUNFIRE ]

125
00:09:09,537 --> 00:09:11,203
THERE'S NO END
TO THESE THINGS.

126
00:09:11,237 --> 00:09:12,703
JUST HANG IN THERE,
EVERYONE.

127
00:09:12,737 --> 00:09:15,237
THE LIGHT OF THE MORNING SUN
WILL MAKE THE DEMONS WEAK.

128
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:16,870
WE'VE GOT TO HOLD OUT
UNTIL THEN.

129
00:09:16,903 --> 00:09:20,370
TILL MORNING?
BUT THE SUN ONLY
JUST WENT DOWN, MAN.

130
00:09:20,403 --> 00:09:22,537
WE CAN'T KEEP THIS UP
FOR LONG.

131
00:09:22,570 --> 00:09:25,370
UM, EXCUSE ME, SIR.
YES, MIWA.
WHAT IS IT?

132
00:09:25,403 --> 00:09:29,170
THE JAPAN BRANCH
IS SUPPOSED TO BE CONNECTED
TO VATICAN HEADQUARTERS, RIGHT?

133
00:09:29,203 --> 00:09:30,770
YEAH. SO WHAT ARE
YOU GETTING AT?

134
00:09:30,803 --> 00:09:33,837
THE TIME DIFFERENCE BETWEEN HERE
AND THE VATICAN IS SEVEN HOURS.

135
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:36,237
HUH? YEAH!

136
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:38,537
OH!
OH? WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "OH"?

137
00:09:38,570 --> 00:09:40,003
I'M TOTALLY LOST HERE.

138
00:09:40,037 --> 00:09:43,537
IF WE USE A MAGIC KEY,
WE CAN EVACUATE TO THE VATICAN.

139
00:09:43,570 --> 00:09:46,803
SINCE IT'S STILL THE MIDDLE
OF THE DAY OVER THERE--

140
00:09:46,837 --> 00:09:47,803
OH.

141
00:09:53,342 --> 00:09:54,609
[ PANTING ]

142
00:09:54,642 --> 00:09:56,409
[ SHIMA ]
AH, YEAH! THE SUN!

143
00:09:56,442 --> 00:09:58,509
[ PAKU ]
GREAT IDEA, MIWA.

144
00:09:58,542 --> 00:10:02,309
NOW ALL WE HAVE TO DO
IS FIGURE OUT HOW TO LURE
THE DEMONS INTO THIS SQUARE.

145
00:10:02,342 --> 00:10:04,942
ACTUALLY, WE DON'T NEED 'EM
TO COME HERE.
HUH?

146
00:10:04,976 --> 00:10:07,342
I'VE GOT AN IDEA.

147
00:10:14,542 --> 00:10:15,942
[ ROARING ]

148
00:10:18,876 --> 00:10:20,842
DAMN IT.
WATCH OUT!

149
00:10:21,876 --> 00:10:23,209
HANG ON TIGHT!

150
00:10:31,242 --> 00:10:32,909
WHOA!

151
00:10:34,976 --> 00:10:36,642
THANKS A LOT, KURO.

152
00:10:36,676 --> 00:10:38,409
HEY, RIN, FOCUS YOUR ATTACK
ON THE GATE.

153
00:10:38,442 --> 00:10:40,176
WITH THEM IN THE WAY?

154
00:10:40,209 --> 00:10:42,576
THEY'RE JUST GONNA BLOCK
MY SHOT AGAIN.

155
00:10:42,609 --> 00:10:44,409
[ SHIMA ]
CREATE A SUN?

156
00:10:44,442 --> 00:10:47,609
[ SUGURO ]
WE'RE GONNA DIRECT THE SUNLIGHT
FROM HERE TO THE JAPAN BRANCH.

157
00:10:47,642 --> 00:10:50,109
THAT WAY WE CAN HELP
EVERYONE THERE...

158
00:10:50,142 --> 00:10:53,342
AND KEEP THOSE THINGS
FROM GETTING TO EVERYONE
HERE AT THE VATICAN.

159
00:10:53,376 --> 00:10:57,342
- WE'RE READY OVER HERE!
- ALL RIGHT.
LET'S DO THIS.

160
00:11:10,109 --> 00:11:10,909
[ GASPING ]

161
00:11:10,942 --> 00:11:12,909
HERE IT COMES!
TAKE COVER!

162
00:11:18,942 --> 00:11:22,109
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT LIGHT?
PRETTY.

163
00:11:22,142 --> 00:11:23,809
[ SHRIEKING ]

164
00:11:25,876 --> 00:11:27,942
THEY'RE DISTRACTED
BY THE LIGHT.

165
00:11:27,976 --> 00:11:31,309
NOW, RIN!
GOT IT!
HERE GOES NOTHING!

166
00:11:40,242 --> 00:11:41,709
[ SHOUTING ]

167
00:11:41,742 --> 00:11:43,542
- <i>RIN!</i>
- RIN!

168
00:11:45,842 --> 00:11:47,309
[ GRUNTING ]

169
00:11:51,942 --> 00:11:54,376
[ GASPS ]
YUKIO!

170
00:11:54,409 --> 00:11:56,309
GRAB ON!

171
00:12:03,209 --> 00:12:04,876
WOW!

172
00:12:08,876 --> 00:12:12,476
- THEY'RE FLYING.
- BRAVO! MAGNIFICENT!

173
00:12:12,509 --> 00:12:16,376
I NEVER DREAMED
THEY'D BE ABLE TO CONTROL
THEIR FLAMES LIKE THAT.

174
00:12:16,409 --> 00:12:20,909
BROTHERS OKUMURA,
YOU ARE EXTRAORDINARY!

175
00:12:20,942 --> 00:12:22,576
YOU READY FOR THIS?

176
00:12:22,609 --> 00:12:24,842
YEAH, LET'S TRASH THAT GATE.

177
00:12:27,976 --> 00:12:30,309
[ BOTH SHOUTING ]

178
00:12:34,542 --> 00:12:36,109
[ SATAN ]
WHY WOULD MY SONS--

179
00:12:36,142 --> 00:12:38,476
MINE AND YURI'S OWN
FLESH AND BLOOD--

180
00:12:38,509 --> 00:12:40,876
WHY WOULD YOU DESTROY OUR DREAM?

181
00:12:40,909 --> 00:12:43,476
WE DON'T GIVE A DAMN
ABOUT YOUR DREAM!

182
00:12:43,509 --> 00:12:45,276
WE JUST WANNA PROTECT--

183
00:12:45,309 --> 00:12:46,742
THE PEOPLE WE CARE ABOUT.

184
00:12:46,776 --> 00:12:48,709
AND THE WORLD WE LIVE IN!

185
00:12:48,742 --> 00:12:51,009
[ BOTH ]
WE'LL ALWAYS PROTECT THEM!

186
00:12:51,876 --> 00:12:55,809
[ SATAN SCREAMING ]

187
00:13:02,442 --> 00:13:04,142
[ GASPING ]

188
00:13:10,742 --> 00:13:12,676
WHAT'S THAT LIGHT?

189
00:13:12,709 --> 00:13:14,842
IT'S WARM, ISN'T IT?

190
00:13:20,409 --> 00:13:22,942
[ THINKING ]
RIN, YUKI.

191
00:13:27,976 --> 00:13:30,576
[ YURI ]
SATAN.

192
00:13:30,609 --> 00:13:34,076
[ SATAN ]
YURI, FORGIVE ME.

193
00:13:34,109 --> 00:13:37,842
I COULDN'T MAKE
YOUR DREAM COME TRUE.

194
00:13:37,876 --> 00:13:40,276
YOU WERE TOO IMPATIENT.

195
00:13:40,309 --> 00:13:44,309
NEITHER OF US KNOWS
IF THE PATH WE CHOSE
WAS THE RIGHT ONE.

196
00:13:44,342 --> 00:13:47,542
THAT'S SOMETHING
FOR OUR CHILDREN
TO FIND OUT FOR US.

197
00:13:57,942 --> 00:13:59,542
[ SHIMA ]
MAN, WHAT A MESS.

198
00:13:59,576 --> 00:14:02,442
[ KAMIKI ]
EVERYTHING'S RUINED.

199
00:14:02,476 --> 00:14:04,509
DO YOU THINK
IT'S ALL OVER?

200
00:14:04,542 --> 00:14:06,376
[ RIN ]
HEY, GUYS!

201
00:14:06,409 --> 00:14:08,709
[ PAKU ]
OKUMURA!

202
00:14:08,742 --> 00:14:11,142
- WHAT UP?
- HEY, THEY'RE ALIVE.

203
00:14:11,176 --> 00:14:13,876
YOU MADE IT BACK
IN ONE PIECE.

204
00:14:13,909 --> 00:14:16,276
YOU ARE SUCH
A FRIGGIN' DUMBASS!

205
00:14:16,309 --> 00:14:19,742
YOU LIKE MAKING US WORRY
ABOUT YOU OR SOMETHING?

206
00:14:19,776 --> 00:14:20,976
[ GASPING ]

207
00:14:21,009 --> 00:14:23,842
WHAT HAPPENED TO SATAN?
HE DEAD?

208
00:14:27,742 --> 00:14:30,342
HE WENT BACK TO GEHENNA,
I GUESS.

209
00:14:30,376 --> 00:14:33,276
BUT THERE'S
A CHANCE
HE'LL BE BACK.

210
00:14:33,309 --> 00:14:36,409
WHO KNOWS?
OH, YEAH?

211
00:14:37,542 --> 00:14:39,342
[ SHIEMI ]
RIN, YUKI!

212
00:14:39,376 --> 00:14:42,109
SHIEMI.

213
00:14:42,142 --> 00:14:44,176
WHAT THE HELL
WERE YOU TWO THINKING?

214
00:14:44,209 --> 00:14:47,609
- HOW COULD YOU BE
SO RECKLESS?
- [ BOTH ] WHOA! BUSTED!

215
00:14:47,642 --> 00:14:50,042
[ BOTH GASP ]

216
00:14:50,076 --> 00:14:54,109
DO ME A FAVOR.
DON'T MAKE ME WORRY
LIKE THAT AGAIN.

217
00:14:57,709 --> 00:14:59,842
WE WON'T.
I PROMISE.

218
00:14:59,876 --> 00:15:01,576
WHAT ARE YOU,
OUR MOM?

219
00:15:01,609 --> 00:15:03,509
[ SHIEMI CRYING ]

220
00:15:06,776 --> 00:15:10,276
TYPICAL!
YOU GUYS ARE ALWAYS
CAUSING TROUBLE.

221
00:15:10,309 --> 00:15:13,142
TAKARA?
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN
THIS WHOLE TIME?

222
00:15:19,042 --> 00:15:21,076
[ AMAIMON ]
THE MINIATURE WORLD
YOU LOVE SO MUCH...

223
00:15:21,109 --> 00:15:22,942
HAS BEEN DESTROYED,
BIG BROTHER.

224
00:15:25,076 --> 00:15:29,109
WHAT'S WRONG?
NO, I WAS JUST REMEMBERING
SOMETHING.

225
00:15:29,142 --> 00:15:33,742
A WAGER I HAD
AND THE MAN WHO ACCEPTED IT
A FEW HUNDRED YEARS AGO.

226
00:15:33,776 --> 00:15:37,076
- WHAT WAGER?
- IT WAS EXTRAORDINARY.

227
00:15:37,109 --> 00:15:39,042
THE STAKES WERE LIFE
OR DEATH.

228
00:15:39,076 --> 00:15:41,909
WHICH OF YOU WON?
I DID, OF COURSE.

229
00:15:41,942 --> 00:15:45,776
I'M THINKING ABOUT WHAT HE SAID
WHEN HE DIED THOUGH.

230
00:15:45,809 --> 00:15:51,309
HE SHOUTED, "STOP, TIME!
THOU ART SO BEAUTIFUL!"

231
00:15:54,709 --> 00:15:57,209
THE WAY YOU FELT
AT THAT MOMENT, SIR,

232
00:15:57,242 --> 00:16:00,376
I BELIEVE I NOW UNDERSTAND
WHAT YOU MEANT.

233
00:16:11,076 --> 00:16:13,909
♪ [ WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

234
00:17:33,876 --> 00:17:37,542
