A MONTH WENT BY,
AND HERE WE ARE.

235
00:17:37,576 --> 00:17:40,042
MEPHISTO--
UH, SCRATCH THAT.

236
00:17:40,076 --> 00:17:43,176
JOHANN FAUST V
WAS BROUGHT BACK
AS DIRECTOR OF THE ACADEMY.

237
00:17:43,209 --> 00:17:46,409
THEY STARTED CLASSES
BACK UP AGAIN TOO.

238
00:17:46,442 --> 00:17:49,742
[ YUKIO ] THE MANDRAKE HAS
BEEN USED AS AN APHRODISIAC
SINCE THE DAYS BEFORE CHRIST.

239
00:17:49,776 --> 00:17:51,542
