240
00:17:51,576 --> 00:17:55,509
NOW YOU HAVE TO BE CAREFUL
WHEN PULLING THE MANDRAKE
OUT OF THE GROUND...

241
00:17:55,542 --> 00:17:57,242
BECAUSE ONCE IT'S OUT--

242
00:17:57,276 --> 00:18:00,842
[ RIN ]
FOR SOME REASON THEY TOOK AWAY
YUKIO'S RANK AS PALADIN.

243
00:18:00,876 --> 00:18:04,009
THEY BUSTED HIM BACK DOWN
TO EXORCIST FIRST CLASS.

244
00:18:04,042 --> 00:18:06,209
I DON'T KNOW ALL THE DETAILS.

245
00:18:06,242 --> 00:18:09,709
I HEARD SOMETHING
ABOUT HUMAN RESOURCES
AND THE VATICAN... STUFF.

246
00:18:09,742 --> 00:18:11,442
[ YAWNING ]

247
00:18:11,476 --> 00:18:15,176
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

248
00:18:15,209 --> 00:18:16,509
[ SHOUTS ]

249
00:18:16,542 --> 00:18:18,909
HUH? HUH?

250
00:18:19,709 --> 00:18:20,809
[ SIGHS ]

251
00:18:23,242 --> 00:18:24,842
[ METALLIC CLANG ]

252
00:18:30,742 --> 00:18:33,609
[ RIN ]
SO WHERE ARE WE GOING?

253
00:18:33,642 --> 00:18:36,076
[ YUKIO ]
I HAVE ABSOLUTELY NO IDEA.

254
00:18:36,109 --> 00:18:39,842
NICE. YOU WANT ME
TO GO WITH YOU,
BUT YOU DON'T KNOW WHERE.

255
00:18:41,809 --> 00:18:44,276
LOOK, THE DIRECTOR
HANDED ME THIS KEY,

256
00:18:44,309 --> 00:18:47,342
THEN HE SAID
WE HAD TO GO TOGETHER.

257
00:18:47,376 --> 00:18:48,842
ALL RIGHT.

258
00:18:52,542 --> 00:18:54,342
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

259
00:18:54,376 --> 00:18:56,376
OH, I GET IT.

260
00:18:56,409 --> 00:18:58,309
WHAT? WAIT.
WHAT DO YOU GET?

261
00:19:03,076 --> 00:19:04,942
RIGHT BEFORE SATAN
POSSESSED ME,

262
00:19:04,976 --> 00:19:08,042
I COULD SEE
ALL HIS MEMORIES
LIKE THEY WERE MINE.

263
00:19:08,076 --> 00:19:09,509
HMM?

264
00:19:10,642 --> 00:19:12,142
IT WAS HERE.

265
00:19:12,176 --> 00:19:16,809
THIS IS THE FOREST
WHERE OUR MOTHER GAVE BIRTH
TO YOU AND ME.

266
00:19:16,842 --> 00:19:18,909
WHERE SHE GAVE
HER LIFE FOR US.

267
00:19:20,442 --> 00:19:22,776
WHOA! WHAT THE HECK?

268
00:19:22,809 --> 00:19:25,809
[ YUKIO ]
SNOWMEN.
A SUBSPECIES OF GOLEMS.

269
00:19:27,742 --> 00:19:29,842
MM.

270
00:19:29,876 --> 00:19:32,842
LET'S GO.
THEY'RE SHOWING US THE WAY.

271
00:19:51,209 --> 00:19:54,009
THAT'S IT.
WE WERE BORN
IN THAT CAVE.

272
00:19:54,042 --> 00:19:55,309
HUH?

273
00:19:57,709 --> 00:20:00,542
ON A SNOWY NIGHT,
OUR DAD FOUND US IN THERE.

274
00:20:02,476 --> 00:20:05,242
MOM LEFT US IN HIS CARE AND--

275
00:20:05,276 --> 00:20:07,309
AND THEN SHE DIED.

276
00:20:13,542 --> 00:20:16,009
IS THAT... OUR MOM?

277
00:20:18,042 --> 00:20:21,009
SO, UH, YOU COULD SEE HER
IN THOSE MEMORIES, RIGHT?

278
00:20:21,042 --> 00:20:25,009
'CAUSE IF YOU DID SEE HER,
THEN WHAT DID SHE LOOK LIKE?

279
00:20:33,709 --> 00:20:36,576
SHE WAS REALLY BEAUTIFUL.

280
00:20:36,609 --> 00:20:37,976
[ GROANING ]

281
00:20:38,009 --> 00:20:41,042
THAT'S ALL YOU GOT?
WHAT ABOUT, LIKE,
I DON'T KNOW.

282
00:20:41,076 --> 00:20:42,509
WERE HER EYES
DOUBLE LIDDED?

283
00:20:42,542 --> 00:20:44,042
RIN.
HMM?

284
00:20:45,376 --> 00:20:46,742
HAVE YOU EVER THOUGHT...

285
00:20:46,776 --> 00:20:49,042
MAYBE IT WASN'T RIGHT
THAT YOU AND I WERE BORN?

286
00:20:51,242 --> 00:20:56,042
IF WE DIDN'T EXIST,
THEN MOM AND DAD WOULD STILL
BE ALIVE RIGHT NOW.

287
00:20:56,076 --> 00:20:59,242
AND ALL OUR FRIENDS--
THEY WOULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN HURT.

288
00:21:01,142 --> 00:21:03,142
YOU'RE SUCH A DORK.
[ GASPS ]

289
00:21:05,009 --> 00:21:07,542
SERIOUSLY? WHAT ABOUT
EVERYTHING THEY BELIEVED?

290
00:21:07,576 --> 00:21:08,942
WHAT ABOUT WHAT THEY STOOD FOR?

291
00:21:08,976 --> 00:21:11,676
IT'S CAUSE OF WHO THEY WERE
THAT WE'RE EVEN HERE.

292
00:21:11,709 --> 00:21:14,509
THEY MADE US WHO WE ARE.
THEY GAVE US OUR LIVES.

293
00:21:16,542 --> 00:21:18,842
[ SIGHS ]
YOU'RE RIGHT.

294
00:21:21,076 --> 00:21:23,742
OUR PARENTS WERE
PRETTY AMAZING,

295
00:21:23,776 --> 00:21:26,942
WEREN'T THEY?
DAMN RIGHT THEY WERE.

296
00:21:28,576 --> 00:21:30,542
[ RIN ]
THEY'RE OUR PARENTS AFTER ALL.

297
00:21:35,376 --> 00:21:38,209
[ MAN #1 ]
WE SEALED OFF TRUE CROSS
JUNCTION AT ROUTE 3.

298
00:21:38,242 --> 00:21:40,509
[ MAN #2 ]
THE SOUTH GATE'S
ON LOCKDOWN AS WELL.

299
00:21:40,542 --> 00:21:45,509
THE ENEMY IS A GHOST-RIDER,
A DEMON THAT POSSESSES CORPSES
AND CAUSES TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS,

300
00:21:45,542 --> 00:21:47,876
SO STAY SHARP, PEOPLE.

301
00:21:50,442 --> 00:21:52,276
HERE IT COMES.

302
00:21:55,776 --> 00:21:57,842
[ ALL ]
HUH?

303
00:22:02,642 --> 00:22:04,609
- WHAT UP?
- [ ALL GASPING ]

304
00:22:04,642 --> 00:22:06,376
WHAT THE--
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

305
00:22:06,409 --> 00:22:08,842
EXWIRES ARE NOT CLEARED
FOR THESE KINDS OF MISSIONS.

306
00:22:08,876 --> 00:22:10,742
AW, DON'T BE SUCH A WUSS.

307
00:22:10,776 --> 00:22:14,976
BROTHERS HAVE TO STICK TOGETHER
AND BACK EACH OTHER UP NO MATTER
WHAT THE RULE BOOK SAYS.

308
00:22:15,009 --> 00:22:17,542
[ YUKIO ]
WOULD YOU GET OUTTA HERE?
THIS IS DANGEROUS.

309
00:22:17,576 --> 00:22:18,876
[ KURO ]
WATCH IT, RIN!

310
00:22:21,909 --> 00:22:23,709
[ REVVING ENGINE ]

311
00:22:23,742 --> 00:22:25,009
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

312
00:22:28,476 --> 00:22:29,509
LOOK OUT!

313
00:22:33,609 --> 00:22:35,776
[ SHOUTING ]

314
00:22:39,309 --> 00:22:40,509
YOU DID IT!

315
00:22:40,542 --> 00:22:42,076
COURSE I DID.
LOOK, RIN.

316
00:22:42,109 --> 00:22:43,476
- [ TRUCK HORN BLARES ]
- [ GASPING ]

317
00:22:51,476 --> 00:22:53,176
OKAY, WHAT'S GOING ON?

318
00:22:53,209 --> 00:22:56,009
THAT IS A TYPE OF DEMON
THAT POSSESSES VEHICLES.

319
00:22:56,042 --> 00:22:58,142
IT JUMPED FROM THE BIKE
TO THAT TRUCK.

320
00:23:00,509 --> 00:23:01,942
CUT IT OUT, YUKIO!

321
00:23:03,976 --> 00:23:06,142
WHY DID YOU GET
IN MY WAY?

322
00:23:06,176 --> 00:23:08,342
