[ GROANS ]
THAT'S A HEADLESS CORPSE,
YOU IDIOT.

324
00:23:13,442 --> 00:23:15,876
WE HAVE TO DESTROY IT
ALONG WITH THE SEMI.

325
00:23:15,909 --> 00:23:17,876
AND WHAT GIVES YOU THE RIGHT
TO MAKE THAT CALL?

326
00:23:17,909 --> 00:23:20,109
IT'S FREAKING OUT
'CAUSE IT DIDN'T GET A FUNERAL.

327
00:23:20,142 --> 00:23:22,509
BUT IF IT'S HURTING HUMANS,
WE HAVE TO DESTROY IT.

328
00:23:22,542 --> 00:23:27,776
YOU'RE WRONG. AN EXORCIST'S JOB
IS TO FIGURE OUT WHAT IT WANTS,
THEN EXORCISE IT.

329
00:23:27,809 --> 00:23:30,742
HELL, THAT'S WHAT
THE OLD MAN WOULD SAY.

330
00:23:30,776 --> 00:23:33,042
OH, RIN.
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

331
00:23:33,076 --> 00:23:35,409
WOULD YOU GUYS
CUT THE CRAP ALREADY?
IT'S COMING.

332
00:23:35,442 --> 00:23:37,409
[ REVVING GROWLS ]

333
00:23:40,109 --> 00:23:42,109
I'LL GET
THAT THING'S ATTENTION.

334
00:23:42,142 --> 00:23:44,842
WHILE I'M KEEPING IT BUSY,
YOU GUYS FIND ITS WEAK SPOT.

335
00:23:44,876 --> 00:23:46,409
COME ON!
NO, WAIT!

336
00:23:46,442 --> 00:23:47,809
[ SHURA ]
HEY!

337
